  # Anmoku å®‰é»™

  <sub>A peaceful and fully typed [MyAnimeList](https://myanimelist.net/) / [Jikan](https://jikan.moe/) Python API wrapper with caching and proper rate limiting.</sub>

  <img width="550px" src="./assets/quick_showcase_1.gif">

